text: Kamchalytamak () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kadyrgulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 475 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 51 km from Davlekanovo, 7 km from Kadyrgulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kamchalytamak
